      "title": "GPT-5.6 used a prompt to close a 30-year gap in convex optimization",
      "url": "https://old.reddit.com/r/math/comments/1uxj3cy/after_openais_cdc_proof_announcement_gpt56_used_a/",
      "discuss_url": "https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=48957779",
      "score": 554,
      "comments": 354,
      "author": "mbustamanter",
      "published": "2026-07-18T13:00:52Z",
      "bullets": [
        "A single prompt enabled GPT-5.6 to resolve a long-standing mathematical bottleneck, demonstrating LLMs' capacity for deep algorithmic discovery.",
        "This success underscores the power of advanced prompting over fine-tuning for solving complex, theoretical computer science and optimization problems.",
        "Practitioners should explore LLM-driven heuristic generation to automate and accelerate algorithmic design in operations research and machine learning pipelines."
      ]
    },
