      "bullets": [
        "Human reviewers suffer from automation bias and fatigue, making them ineffective at catching subtle logical bugs in high-volume AI-generated code.",
        "Tools like GitHub Copilot generate vast amounts of syntactically correct boilerplate, overwhelming standard PR review processes and masking architectural flaws.",
        "Engineers must shift-left with rigorous CI/CD, SAST scanning, and comprehensive unit tests rather than relying on human QA of LLM outputs."
      ]
